title: The Little Mermaid Controversy
description:
Tune in to Camo’s weekly recap before they dive into the new live action Little Mermaid drama. Stick around for the fan Q&A at the end!
For 50% off your first Care/of order, go to TakeCareOf.com and enter code “unfazed50”.
Get $100 off your first month at Talkspace.com with code UNFAZED.
Sign-up for a Chime Checking Account at chime.com/unfazed.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
